apogee contains the python routines written for APOGEE
pyvista is a subtree from holtzmanjon/pyvista, with the tv module (and some reduction utilities, not used)
tools is a subtree from holtzmanjon/tools, with some plotting utilities

To add a remote and use it as a subtree:
git remote add tools https://github.com/holtzmanjon/tools
git subtree add --prefix python/tools tools master --squash

